      "type": "text",
      "title": "Service directory",
      "gridPos": { "h": 16, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 13 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Inference — vLLM coder (Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B-Instruct-AWQ)\n\n- [API root](http://luna:8000/) · [`/v1/models`](http://luna:8000/v1/models) · [`/v1/chat/completions`](http://luna:8000/v1/chat/completions) (POST)\n- [`/docs` (Swagger)](http://luna:8000/docs) · [`/redoc`](http://luna:8000/redoc)\n- [`/metrics`](http://luna:8000/metrics) · [`/health`](http://luna:8000/health)\n- OpenAI-compatible base URL → `http://luna:8000/v1`\n\n## Observability\n\n- Dashboards: [claude-code](/d/claude-code) · [luna-stack](/d/luna-stack)\n- [Prometheus UI](http://luna:9090/) · [`/-/healthy`](http://luna:9090/-/healthy) · [`/targets`](http://luna:9090/targets) · [`/rules`](http://luna:9090/rules) · [`/alerts`](http://luna:9090/alerts)\n- [OTel collector → Prom exporter](http://luna:8889/metrics)\n- OTLP intake: gRPC `luna:4317` · HTTP `luna:4318` (no UI)\n- Loki HTTP API: `http://luna:3100/` (query via Grafana Explore → Loki datasource)\n- Pushgateway: [`http://luna:9091/`](http://luna:9091/) — open per `openFirewall = true`\n\n## Pipeline (paths, not URLs)\n\n- Ingest log: `~/Repositories/ocasazza/obsidian/scripts/ingest.log`\n- Reingest log: `~/Repositories/ocasazza/obsidian/scripts/reingest-auto.log`\n- Textfile collector dir (luna): `/var/lib/node_exporter/textfile/`\n- Reingest metrics file: `/var/lib/node_exporter/textfile/reingest.prom`\n- Trigger one-shot reingest: `~/Repositories/ocasazza/obsidian/scripts/reingest-auto.sh`\n\n## Docs\n\n- Vault architecture: `~/Repositories/ocasazza/obsidian/CLAUDE.md`\n- Observability nix module: `~/.config/nixos-config/modules/nixos/observability/default.nix`\n- luna host config: `~/.config/nixos-config/systems/x86_64-linux/luna/default.nix`\n- vLLM module: `~/.config/nixos-config/modules/nixos/vllm/default.nix`\n- luna-stack panel design notes: `~/.config/nixos-config/modules/nixos/observability/dashboards/luna-stack-panels.md`\n\n## Hostnames\n\nUse bare `luna` (192.168.1.57) — confirmed working from LAN clients. `luna.local` (Avahi/mDNS) publishes from the host but does not currently resolve from this Mac; investigate Bonjour cache or interface routing if needed.\n"
      }
